{"tid":1921612,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【討論】我哋目標應該係打倒中國土地同人民頭上嘅政權(共產黨)，而唔係中國本體。","createTime":"2020-03-12T05:39:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-12T09:10:09.000Z","uid":128883,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9746779510766645e1615db8a6b6cb5c00d8f89f","tid":1921612,"uid":128883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:39:09.000Z","msg":"你要打到中國成個國家土地同人民，除非用核彈。<br />\n<br />\n所以冇意思，亦都不切實際。<br />\n<br />\n我嘅意思係全世界排華浪潮蒞臨之前。<br />\n<br />\n我哋要做好文宣工作，大家目標係中國嘅共產黨，而唔係中國或者中國人。<br />\n<br />\n如果真係發生排華浪潮，對我哋香港人都冇好處。<br />\n<br />\n難道外國人會分得出香港人同中國人？"},{"pid":"e0f363da74f84589ffe01df9e365401731979b16","tid":1921612,"uid":128883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:56:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4616d060b0d083d53d117365e3ed3b1aad2619da","tid":1921612,"uid":128883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:58:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4e3b0f1a99eeb0416c7d0654bac6209012a499d","tid":1921612,"uid":128883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:58:41.000Z","msg":"3連推"},{"pid":"ce27390678714ecfba30f7df4457300dbe26f110","tid":1921612,"uid":128883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:58:54.000Z","msg":"4連推"},{"pid":"3a3b4e27cab0a576e823ffff5dc21a53822f86d1","tid":1921612,"uid":128883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:59:10.000Z","msg":"5連推"},{"pid":"5f086b1ffcaeb0452d729f245b3cca08bb3b29d7","tid":1921612,"uid":128883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:59:33.000Z","msg":"6連推"},{"pid":"bbb7e527267ac499c9efca535ad2e9198b81c555","tid":1921612,"uid":128883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T05:59:44.000Z","msg":"7連推"},{"pid":"4a707051f9565fe12e3cedf87d8b5f5270a778d3","tid":1921612,"uid":128883,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-12T06:00:08.000Z","msg":"8連推"},{"pid":"4a803d16ba765